results.name: Row sums of lower triangular matrix A093662.
comment: a(n) equals the number of sequences of length A000120(n-1) that satisfy an ordering restriction (cf. A016121), where A000120(n-1) is the number of 1's in the binary expansion of n-1.
results.author: _Paul D. Hanna_, Apr 08 2004
